The paper discusses the role of search engines in retrieving meaningful information from the large database repositories available on the World Wide Web. This topic is closely related to information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), databases (cs.DB), software engineering (cs.SE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
